<\body>
  <doc-data|<doc-title|A Riemann-Hilbert approach to skew-orthogonal
  polynomials of symplectic type>|<doc-author|<author-data|<author-name|Alex
  Little>|<author-email|alexander.little@ens-lyon.fr>|<\author-affiliation>
    Unité de Mathématiques Pures et Appliquées

    ENS de Lyon
  </author-affiliation>|<author-affiliation|Electronic
  address:>>>|<doc-date|<date|>>|<doc-note|The author would like to express
  his gratitude to Thomas Bothner and Mattia Cafasso, whose comments and
  suggestions have been invaluable for this paper. This work was supported by
